      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Order-of-accuracy test or manufacturer verification documentation sufficient for MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "Vendor-supplied verification benchmarks for incompressible Navier-Stokes and scalar transport demonstrate correct order of accuracy. No bespoke solver modifications were made, so manufacturer documentation is accepted at MRL 2."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
