      "rationale": "The normalized index of hemolysis and volume-averaged scalar shear stress are the primary QoIs. Both are directly used in regulatory hemolysis risk assessment per FDA guidance and ASTM F1841. Their relevance to the worst-case operating condition identification decision is documented in the assessment plan."
