      "rationale": "Validation performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump, which is the same geometry as the subject device model. Operating conditions span the clinical CPB flow range (3–6 L/min, 2000–3000 RPM), confirming relevance of validation activities to the intended operating envelope."
